---
title: Forbidden Rice Salad with Roasted Butternut Squash, Pistachios, and Arugula
description: This Wintery black rice salad is hearty, delicious, and packs a major nutritional punch. We’ve added roasted butternut squash, pistachios, and arugula to this delicious grain. A tangy honey vinaigrette pulls it all together.
